bkzFSZ"><p class="sc-59b6826e-0 kyYvag">In-ear</p></td></tr><tr class="sc-dfa23c87-0 dkdsfi"><td class="sc-fe2e4cbb-0 btUfxD"><p class="sc-59b6826e-0 kKRPYO">Signalübertragung</p></td><td class="sc-fe2e4cbb-0 fRBvcN mms-ui-cXdxXm mms-ui-bkzFSZ"><p class="sc-59b6826e-0 kyYvag">Bluetooth, kabellos</p></td></tr><tr class="sc-dfa23c87-0 dkdsfi"><td class="sc-fe2e4cbb-0 btUfxD"><p class="sc-59b6826e-0 kKRPYO">Noise cancelling</p></td><td class="sc-fe2e4cbb-0 fRBvcN mms-ui-cXdxXm mms-ui-bkzFSZ"><p class="sc-59b6826e-0 kyYvag">aktiv (ANC)</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table class="sc-eb5d0dd3-0 brREjs"><thead class="sc-4d4fd441-0 fAxnSG"><tr class="sc-dfa23c87-0 dkdsfi"><th colSpan="2" class="sc-fe2e4cbb-0 dOdMfy"><p class="sc-59b6826e-0 bxEpDs">Ausstattung</p></th></tr></thead><tbody class="sc-b388eff-0 eqyplR"><tr class="sc-dfa23c87-0 dkdsfi"><td class="sc-fe2e4cbb-0 btUfxD"><p class="sc-59b6826e-0 kKRPYO">Integriertes Mikrofon</p></td><td class="sc-fe2e4cbb-0 fRBvcN mms-ui-cXdxXm mms-ui-bkzFSZ"><p class="sc-59b6826e-0 kyYvag">Ja</p></td></tr><tr class="sc-dfa23c87-0 dkdsfi"><td class="sc-fe2e4cbb-0 btUfxD"><p class="sc-59b6826e-0 kKRPYO">Steuerung</p></td><td class="sc-fe2e4cbb-0 fRBvcN mms-ui-cXdxXm mms-ui-bkzFSZ"><p class="sc-59b6826e-0 kyYvag">An der Hörmuschel</p></td></tr><tr class="sc-dfa23c87-0 dkdsfi"><td class="sc-fe2e4cbb-0 btUfxD"><p class="sc-59b6826e-0 kKRPYO">Headsetfunktion</p></td><td class="sc-fe2e4cbb-0 fRBvcN mms-ui-cXdxXm mms-ui-bkzFSZ"><p class="sc-59b6826e-0 kyYvag">Ja</p></td></tr><tr class="sc-dfa23c87-0 dkdsfi"><td class="sc-fe2e4cbb-0 btUfxD"><p class="sc-59b6826e-0 kKRPYO">Beschleunigungssensor</p></td><td class="sc-fe2e4cbb-0 fRBvcN mms-ui-cXdxXm mms-ui-bkzFSZ"><p class="sc-59b6826e-0 kyYvag">Ja</p></td></tr><tr class="sc-dfa23c87-0 dkdsfi"><td class="sc-fe2e4cbb-0 btUfxD"><p class="sc-59b6826e-0 kKRPYO">Bluetooth</p></td><td class="sc-fe2e4cbb-0 fRBvcN mms-ui-cXdxXm mms-ui-bkzFSZ"><p class="sc-59b6826e-0 kyYvag">Ja</p></td></tr><tr class="sc